Job.create!(title: "Artisan Jeweler", description: "Our jewelery is crafted in the mokume game-style. Mokume gane is an ancient Japanese technique that bonds numerous layers of precious metals into a single piece that is then worked into beautiful patterns. The name means 'wood-pattern metal'. Mokume gane created by Chris Ploof Designs is fused by traditional methods, using heat and pressure. We don’t buy mokume from other makers, and we don’t rely on solder to hold our layers together. By hand-crafting our mokume, we are able to produce the highest quality rings, second to none. Our unique patterns and designs showcase the natural beauty of the material itself.", company: "Chris Ploof Designs", location: "Nolita, NY", jobtype: "Contractual Work");
Job.create!(title: "Caterer", description: "No matter what your special event is... wedding, anniversary, seasonal party, birthday, bar/bat mitzvah and everything in between, Brent Newsom Caterer is the perfect choice to make sure every aspect of your experience goes exactly as you imagined it. Our staff and services can create any theme and menu you desire. Contact us today for great party ideas and creative answers to your catering needs.", company: "Brent Newsom Caterer", location: "East Hampton, NY", jobtype: "Contractual Work");
